N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 198.7 - Disposal

State Regulations

In the event that the Outdoor Recreation and Trail

Maintenance Pin and Patch Program is terminated, any such pins, patches and
associated promotional posters in the possession of the department at such time
may be disposed of at the department's discretion. Notes
